boofcv.android

Class ImplConvertBitmap

  • java.lang.Object
    • boofcv.android.ImplConvertBitmap

  • public class ImplConvertBitmap
extends java.lang.Object
    Low level implementations of Bitmap conversion routines. Contains functions which are not being used for benchmarking purposes. When converting into 565 format a lookup table is used. The equations used to compute the table round instead of flooring to minimize error. I believe that this is what the Android library does too, without looking at the code.
